\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Use 
\f0\b Model A only
\f1\b0 :\
One benchmark task is handled by one autonomous OpenCode session.\
The control loop lives inside the selected OpenCode agent\'92s instructions. The external runner is responsible only for preparing the task, invoking OpenCode, enforcing limits, capturing outputs, and running the benchmark evaluator.\
There is no external multi-agent state machine in this phase.\
