\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 Implementation Through OpenCode\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 OpenCode should be used to build this project incrementally.\
Give OpenCode this plan and ask it to implement only the current milestone.\
Recommended sequence:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Implementation task 1\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs26 \cf0 Implement Milestone 1 only.\
\
Create the minimal runner needed to prepare one benchmark task, invoke OpenCode non-interactively from inside the task repository, capture the resulting git diff and logs, run the benchmark evaluator, and save the result.\
\
Do not implement subsets, feedback-only agents, multi-agent orchestration, or later milestones.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Implementation task 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 After Milestone 1 works:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs26 \cf0 Implement Milestone 2 only.\
\
Add support for a fixed task subset, sequential isolated execution, failure handling, and collection of task success, model cost, and wall-clock runtime.\
\
Do not implement the feedback-only configuration yet.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Implementation task 3\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 After the vanilla subset is stable:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs26 \cf0 Implement Milestone 3 only.\
\
Add a separate feedback-only OpenCode configuration that instructs one agent session to implement, run relevant tests, inspect failures, repair, and repeat within explicit stopping limits.\
\
Run the same fixed task subset used by the vanilla baseline. Preserve the same model and environment settings.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 OpenCode should not be asked to implement the entire roadmap in one pass. Each milestone should be verified before the next is introduced.\
\

